    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>God&apos;s Reward for the Daniels of Today</strong>&mdash;There is now need of men who, like Daniel, will do and dare. A pure heart and a strong, fearless hand are wanted in the world today. God designed that man should be constantly improving, daily reaching a higher point in the scale of excellence. He will help us if we seek to help ourselves. Our hope of happiness in two worlds depends upon our improvement in one....",
